**Mario J. Lucero**, is the cofounder and CEO of [[Heaven_Sent_Gaming]] alongside his high-school sweetheart Isabel Ruiz, and Bitcoin evangelist.

He developed a well-recieved early Bitcoin pseudogame/website, called BitDonate (1.1), which encouraged donations to charities and worthy causes such as the Red Cross and OpenStreetMaps.

